OL,3,CChurch told about allegation of abuse
OL,4,Csix years before priest became bishop
OL,6,FAn allegation of abuse against a
OL,7,Fpriest appeared to have been made six
OL,8,Fyears before he became the Bishop of
OL,9,FSwansea and Brecon.
OL,11,FThe Church in Wales was made aware of
OL,12,Fa complaint about priest Anthony
OL,13,FPierce's conduct against a person
OL,14,Fbelieved to be under the age of 18, in
OL,15,F1993.
OL,17,FHe was later elected as Bishop of
OL,18,FSwansea and Brecon in 1999 and served
OL,19,Funtil 2008.
