OL,3,CChurch told about allegation of abuse
OL,4,Csix years before priest became bishop
OL,6,FIn a letter to the Diocses, the
OL,7,Fcurrent Bishop of Swansea and Brecon,
OL,8,FJohn Lomas said, "We know that in 1993
OL,9,Fanother discourse was made in relation
OL,10,Fto the conduct of Anthony Pierce".
OL,12,FThe allegation against Pierce was
OL,13,Freported to police 17 years later, in
OL,14,F2010.
OL,16,FHowever, South Wales Police were
OL,17,Funable to investigate the claims
OL,18,Fbecause the alleged victim had died.
