OL,3,CChurch told about allegation of abuse
OL,4,Csix years before priest became bishop
OL,6,FThis allegation has come to light
OL,7,Fafter Pierce pleaded guilty in
OL,8,FFebruary of this year to multiple
OL,9,Fcounts of sexually abusing a child at
OL,10,FSwansea Crown Court, in a separate
OL,11,Fcase.
OL,13,FThe Church in Wales has launched a
OL,14,Freview into Pierce's appointment,
OL,15,Fwhich it says "seeks to establish who
OL,16,Fwithin the Church received relevant
OL,17,Finformation, and what they did with
OL,18,Fit."
