OL,3,CChurch told about allegation of abuse
OL,4,Csix years before priest became bishop
OL,6,FIn early February 2025, Anthony Pierce
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty at Swansea Crown Court
OL,8,Fto abuse in the 1980s whilst he was a
OL,9,Fparish priest in the West Cross area
OL,10,Fof Swansea.
OL,12,FPierce, who was the Bishop between
OL,13,F1999 and 2008, pleaded guilty to five
OL,14,Fcounts of indecent assault on a boy
OL,15,Funder 16 years of age when he appeared
OL,16,Fat Swansea Crown Court.
OL,18,FSince then, it has emerged the Church
OL,19,Fwas aware of a separate allegation of
OL,20,Fabuse against him made in 1993.
