OL,3,CChurch told about allegation of abuse
OL,4,Csix years before priest became bishop
OL,6,FThe allegation was passed to South
OL,7,FWales Police in 2010, seventeen years
OL,8,Fafter it was made.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the force said,
OL,11,F"Sadly, in this specific case the
OL,12,Fvictim had passed away in 2010 when
OL,13,Fallegations were made of abuse taking
OL,14,Fplace in 1993.
OL,16,F"Therefore we are not able to progress
OL,17,Fthe investigation".
