OL,3,CChurch told about allegation of abuse
OL,4,Csix years before priest became bishop
OL,6,FThe Church in Wales has launched a
OL,7,Freview into "the handling of an
OL,8,Fallegation of abuse against the Right
OL,9,FReverend Anthony Pierce, first
OL,10,Freported in 1993."
OL,12,FThe Chair of the Church in Wales
OL,13,FSafeguarding Committee has appointed
OL,14,Fan "independent lay person" to carry
OL,15,Fout the review.
OL,17,FIt added, "The Reviewer is not asked
OL,18,Fto review matters concerning an
OL,19,Fallegation against Mr Pierce reported
OL,20,Fto the Church in Wales Safeguarding
OL,21,FTeam and South Wales Police in 2023."
